Tee Hee )))  I have grouped often with the guild but I think that I may have messed up due to not knowing the new looting rules. I have played in LGuk from level 30 on up to where I am now and they never had loot set up to who ever needs what got what ever dropped. EVERY drop was lottoed to whom ever won the lotto, regardless of your class. I spoke with Tiny and Vyktor concerning my adventure in Karnor recently and I was concerned as to why I was not involved in getting any of the drops. I made my concern known and I am praying that my concern did not rub anyone the wrong way. I have NEVER till now played with anyone who gave loot away only to those that could have used it. That being said. I am sorry for my ignorance and maybe everyone can understand that I meant no harm. I just felt out of the picture at the time and did not know what to think about it and felt bad because all of the loot went to everyone else... If anyone wants to group with me, Rosey is camped in Skyfire and will be till I can get some spells. If anyone needs my help in any adventure, feel free to let me know, I will help if I can at the moment... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
